          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "MWPC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Two position-sensitive MWPCs were used for",
                "       detecting both fission fragments in",
                "       coincidence. The MWPC consists of a gold coated",
                "       mylar foil, which is sandwiched by two grounded",
                "       wire planes. The wire planes were made of",
                "       stretched gold-coated tungsten wires with a 2",
                "       mm pitch. The active area of the MWPC is 200 mm",
                "       in horizontal and 120 mm in vertical direction.",
                "       The entrance windows of the MWPC were made of",
                "       Mylar films of 3 micro m thickness."
              ]
            }
          ],
